settings.tooltipFunction:
var alarmStatus = data['alarm'];
var consumption = parseInt(data['energyConsumption']);
if (alarmStatus == 'true') {
    return `<b style="color: red"> 
    <b>Reading: ${consumption} kwh <b/><br />
    <b> Status : Current reading is higher then thresholds(90 KWH)</b> <b></b>`;
